\"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"allocation\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"beds\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"the innovations\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"level\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"this team\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will ensure that whatever is required to make them comfortable, we are [there] to [answer] their call - and we will have that done within the shortest time.\\\"\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 1004, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"their call\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"the shortest time\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kelly says there is no air conditioning in the Jamaicans' rooms at the village, but they have been promised by the organisers that this will not affect them.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"score\": 0.9794504129374556, \"rank\": 0.020980699477922585, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 1053, \"end\": 1062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9999593853095812, \"rank\": 2.085864948357418e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaicans\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no air conditioning\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisers\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are fans,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The rooms are relatively cool.\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The rooms\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think the cooling system that has been put in place, while it is not driven by air conditioning, is pretty cool at night.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cooling system\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"air conditioning\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They [organisers] have made some recommendations with respect to how we use the blinds in the days and cooling at nights.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"some recommendations\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"the blinds\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"the days\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"nights\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So far, we have been having hot days but the buildings are cool and the airflow is pretty good.\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hot days\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"the buildings\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"the airflow\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would think that they would have considered many of these things, hence the reason why air conditioning is not in the rooms.\\\"\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": [], \"