 2024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The truth is, like anything else with new buildings, new constructions, there are some teething pains.\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The truth\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"new buildings\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2088}, {\"ngram\": \"new constructions\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"some teething pains\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thus far, what is important to us within the Jamaican delegation is that the local organising committee is responding to the issues we have raised with them.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2297, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2185, \"end\": 2193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.942784245578697, \"rank\": 0.06031872651455439, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2173}, {\"ngram\": \"the local organising committee\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2243}, {\"ngram\": \"the issues\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The village is quite nice.\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The village\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a modern village, it has modern facilities, and it has modern amenities.\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a modern village\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2349}, {\"ngram\": \"modern facilities\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2375}, {\"ngram\": \"modern amenities\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that where there are gaps, the Jamaican delegation will ensure that those gaps are filled and we will have a great Olympics.\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2538, \"entities\": 